00:00:58.072 --> 00:01:02.095
"How can you guys allow the same people
to terrorize you for 51 years?

00:01:02.119 --> 00:01:04.905
You know, like, you Togolese,
you must be very patient."

00:01:04.929 --> 00:01:07.580
That's their diplomatic way
of saying "stupid."

00:01:07.604 --> 00:01:09.238
(Laughter)

